Program: Outlook
Title: 22/09/2011
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00k5f06
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 26 Sep 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, Pakistani politician Imran Khan on how cricket prepared him for politics. Also the wheelchair dancers of Almaty in Kazakhstan - they rehearse in the street with music from a car stereo. And, Ghalia Alia Mahmoud, the former maid who's found fame as a television cook in Egypt. Show less